{{Infobox magazine | title = CFO | logo = CFO_Magazine_Logo.png | logo_size = | image_file = <!-- cover.jpg (omit the "file: prefix --> | image_size = <!-- (defaults to user thumbnail size if no size is stated) --> | image_alt = | image_caption = | editor = | editor_title = | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | photographer = | category = Trade magazine | frequency = Monthly | circulation = | publisher = | founder = | founded = 1985 | firstdate = <!-- {{Start date|year|month|day}} --> | company = Argyle Executive Forum | country = [[United States]] | based = New York | language = English | website = {{URL|http://www.cfo.com}} | issn = | oclc = }}
'''''CFO''''' is a monthly magazine published in the United States. It was launched in 1985 for [[chief financial officer]]s (CFOs) and other financial executives in companies in the U.S. [[The Economist Group]] acquired the magazine in 1988 and sold it in 2010 to the [[private equity firm]] Seguin Partners.<ref>{{cite news|title=Seguin Partners acquires CFO Publishing from The Economist Group|url=http://www.economistgroup.com/our_news/press_releases/2010/seguin_partners_acquires_cfo_publishing_from_the_economist_group.html|accessdate=18 November 2015|work=The Economist Group}}</ref> In 2016, CFO was bought from Sequin Partners by Argyle Executive Forum, an events business that brings business information and thought leadership to leading professionals from Fortune 1000 companies in North America, Europe, Asia and Australia.<ref>http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20160504006290/en/Argyle-Acquires-Innovation-Enterprise-Leading-High-Touch-Engagement</ref>
It carries a mixture of regional and global content aimed at CFOs and other decision makers in their respective industries. ''CFO'' magazine reaches 440,000 individually qualified readers.<ref>[http://www.echo-media.com/mediaDetail.php?ID=9910 Echo Media about the magazine]</ref> The magazine is a requested, [[Magazine#Controlled_circulation|controlled-circulation]] title so all registered readers are senior level financial decision makers who have requested the magazine. ''CFO''s circulation is audited by [[BPA Worldwide]] with a monthly unique audience of 440,000 users. Advertisers include banks, technology firms, consulting firms, accounting firms, travel services companies, and other companies providing business services.
