'''Georg Kraus''' (born July 30, 1965) is a [[Germany|German]] management consultant and writer;<ref name=praxis>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.fr/books?id=Wo7pCQAAQBAJ&pg=PT291|title=Praxiswissen Management|last1=Nöllke|first1=Matthias|last2=Zielke|first2=Christian|last3=Kraus|first3=Georg|language=German|year=2015|publisher=Haufe Lexware|isbn=978-3648070147|page=3|via=Google Books}}</ref><ref name=medien>{{cite book|url=
https://books.google.fr/books?id=AZ5o2qzMXI4C&pg=PR9&lpg|title=Digitale Medien im Unternehmen: Perspektiven des betrieblichen Einsatzes von neuen Medien|editor-last1=Lembke|editor-first1=Gerald|editor-last2=Soyez|editor-first2=Nadine|year=2012|page=IX|publisher=Springer-Verlag|isbn=978-3642299056|via=Google Books}}</ref><ref name=claus />  ,<ref name=jdn>{{cite web|url=https://www.journaldunet.com/management/direction-generale/change-management/georg-kraus-dr-kraus-parner.shtml|title= "Dans les entreprises actuelles, on ne peut plus se fier à ce qui a été dit la veille"|trans-title= "In today's businesses, we can no longer rely on what was said the day before"|last1=Varin|first1=Claire-Marine|last2=Renou|first2=Fabien|language=French|publisher=Le Journal du Net|date=June 4, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608055622/http://www.journaldunet.com/management/direction-generale/change-management/georg-kraus-dr-kraus-parner.shtml|archivedate=June 8, 2013|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref>    <ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.focus.de/finanzen/karriere/management/tid-10242/change-management-zehn-tipps-fuer-frischen-wind-im-betrieb_aid_306842.html|title= Zehn Tipps für frischen Wind im Betrieb|trans-title= Ten tips for fresh wind in operation|last=Kraus|first=Georg|date=June 6, 2018|language=German|work=[[Focus (German magazine)|Focus]]|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924052653/http://www.focus.de:80/finanzen/karriere/management/tid-10242/change-management-zehn-tipps-fuer-frischen-wind-im-betrieb_aid_306842.html|archivedate=September 24, 2015|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref>   the founder of the Dr. Kraus & Partner consulting company.<ref name=cio />

==Education==
Kraus received a [[bachelor's degree]] at [[Lycée Kléber]] at [[Strasbourg]] and continued his education at the [[Karlsruhe Institute of Technology]], earning a [[Doctor of Science]] degree in 1995.<ref name=karls /> He started his business career in 1987 working for [[Daimler AG]] as an internal strategy and project management consultant<ref name=jdn /><ref name="welt">{{cite web|url=http://expertensuche.welt.de/Fuehrungskompetenz/|title=Führungskompetenz-Experten|year=2016|publisher=[[Die Welt]]|language=German|trans-title=Leadership Experts|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325210527/http://expertensuche.welt.de:80/fuehrungskompetenz/|archivedate=March 25, 2016|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref> (his doctorate [[thesis]] was about employee [[job satisfaction]] in the [[automotive industry]]).<ref name=karls /> The same year he founded the Dr. Kraus & Partner consulting company.{{cn|date=June 2018}}

==Career==
Kraus started his academic career in 1994, becoming a lecturer at the Karlsruhe Institute of Technology<ref name=claus>{{cite web|url= https://www.tu-clausthal.de/presse/nachrichten/details/1855.html|title= Dr. Georg Kraus zum Honorarprofessor bestellt|trans-title= Dr. Georg Kraus appointed honorary professor|language=German|date=June 2, 2015|publisher=[[Clausthal University of Technology]]|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150607080913/https://www.tu-clausthal.de/presse/nachrichten/details/1855.html|archivedate=June 7, 2015|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref> where he taught a change management course.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wiwi.kit.edu/downloads/2010ws_mhb_tvwl_MSc_lang_de.pdf|title=Modulhandbuch Technische Volkswirtschaftslehre (M.Sc.)|trans-title=Technical Economics Modules Handbook (M.Sc.)|date=September 23, 2010|publisher=[[Karlsruhe Institute of Technology]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130210324/http://www.wiwi.kit.edu:80/downloads/2010ws_mhb_tvwl_MSc_lang_de.pdf|archivedate=January 30, 2012|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref> In 1995, together with Reinhold Westermann, he published a project management textbook named ''Projektmanagement mit System'' that has been reprinted 5 times.<ref>{{cite book|title=Management von Projekten: Planung, Durchführung, Überwachung und Steuerung von Projekten in Theorie und Praxis|last=Springer|first= Alexander|publisher=Examicus Publishing|language=German|year=2012|isbn=978-3-86746-865-7|page=4}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Mediengestütztes Bildungsmanagement: Virtuelle Lernwelten für Unternehmen|last=Jörg|first=Sander|year=2013|isbn= 978-3-8244-9008-0|publisher=Deutscher Universitätsverlag|language=German|page=175}}</ref> In 2004, together with Christel Becker-Kolle and Thomas Fischer, he co-authored a handbook on [[change management]].<ref>{{cite book|title=Change 2.0: Beyond Organisational Transformation|editor-last1=Klewes|editor-first1=Joachim|editor-last2=Langen|editor-first2=Ralf|year=2008|isbn=978-3-540-77494-5|doi= 10.1007/978-3-540-77495-2|publisher=Springer-Verlag Berlin Heidelberg|page=115}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Fast Cultural Change: The Role and Influence of Middle Management|last=Nieswand|first=Martina|year=2015|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan UK|isbn=978-1-137-51549-0|doi=10.1057/9781137515506|page=284}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Die 7 Disziplinen im Sales-Management: Eine Anleitung für nachhaltige Kunden- und Geschäftsentwicklung im Vertrieb|last=Rauch|first=Nikolaus A.|year=2016|publisher=Gabler Verlag|language=German|isbn=978-3-658-04231-8|doi=10.1007/978-3-658-04232-5|page=161}}</ref>

Kraus also taught at [[IAE Aix-en-Provence]] (since 2004),<ref name=claus /> the [[Clausthal University of Technology]] (since 2005)<ref name=claus /> and the St. Galler Business School (since 2007).<ref name=claus /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://sgbs.ch/ueber_uns/dozentenstab/dr_georg_kraus/|title=Dr. Georg Kraus|year=2017|publisher= St. Galler Business School|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20170821004424/http://sgbs.ch/ueber_uns/dozentenstab/dr_georg_kraus/|archivedate=August 21, 2017|accessdate=May 6, 2018}}</ref> In 2015 he was appointed [[Honorary title (academic)|honorary professor]] at the Faculty of Energy and Economics at [[Clausthal University of Technology]].<ref name=claus /> While working at IAE Aix-en-Provence he initiated the European Change Forum (held annually since 2012).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.laprovence.com/actu/leco-en-direct/1775510/eco-agenda-forum-change-management-a-liae.html|title=Eco Agenda: "Forum Change Management" à l'IAE|trans-title=Eco Agenda: "Forum Change Management" at IAE|language=French|date=June 5, 2012|newspaper=[[La Provence]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180504213406/https://www.laprovence.com/actu/leco-en-direct/1775510/eco-agenda-forum-change-management-a-liae.html|archivedate=May 4, 2018|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iaeaixalumni.org/event/european-change-forum/2013/06/21/169|title=European Change Forum|author=Antje Vogdt|date=June 21, 2013|website= iaeaixalumni.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180504214837/http://www.iaeaixalumni.org/event/european-change-forum/2013/06/21/169|archivedate=May 4, 2018|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref>

Kraus supports low-income entrepreneurs and students through the [[Kiva (organization)|Kiva]] micro loans website<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/59668048e4b051f16255e585|title=Micro Loans - Helping people help themselves|author=Maja Tisma|date=July 12, 2017|publisher=[[HuffPost]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509202705/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/59668048e4b051f16255e585|archivedate=May 9, 2018|accessdate=May 9, 2018}}</ref> and serves as a member of the board of trustees of [[Heinrich Pesch House|Heinrich Pesch Foundation]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://heinrich-pesch-haus.de/heinrich-pesch-stiftung-gegruendet/|title= Heinrich-Pesch-Stiftung gegründet|trans-title=Heinrich Pesch Foundation founded|year=2016|language=German|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613162326/http://heinrich-pesch-haus.de/heinrich-pesch-stiftung-gegruendet/|archivedate=June 13, 2016|accessdate=May 9, 2018}}</ref>

